---
// Footer — thin top border, 11px italic disclaimer + contact + © line.
// Per STYLE_GUIDE.md / PRD.md: this disclaimer appears on every page.
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <p class="disclaimer">
    The Corn is a satirical publication. All persons, businesses, and events
    depicted are fictional or fictionalized. Any resemblance to actual residents
    or local establishments is coincidental and affectionate.
  </p>
  <p class="meta">
    Corrections, complaints, or takedown requests:
    <a href="mailto:corrections@thecorn.ca">corrections@thecorn.ca</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
    <span>&copy; 2026 The Corn</span>
  </p>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    margin-top: 4em;
    padding: 1.5em 0 3em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .disclaimer {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 0 0.6em;
  }

  .meta {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .meta a {
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
</style>
